title: Alcoholics Anonymous Has Been Forced Online Due To The Coronavirus
description: AA members are concerned for people in early recovery, who might not have the support network in place to help prevent a relapse during this pandemic. View Entire Post ›
content:
"I would not want to be in early recovery right now," Matthew told BuzzFeed News.
